    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Datadog is not showing this as a very common failure on `main`. Considering how infrequent it is, I am going to close this out for now. If this reappears, the additional logs from https://github.com/coder/coder/pull/13818 will aid in debugging.\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2024-07-10 09-32-05](https://github.com/coder/coder/assets/5446298/5ce2f774-edc8-46e1-9a59-48c45564cca3)\r\n\r\n\r\nReopen if this flakes on `main` :+1: ",
